import React from 'react'
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom'
import './index.css'
import App from './App'
import { ProductsProvider } from './context/products_context'
import { FilterProvider } from './context/filter_context'

ReactDOM.render(

    <ProductsProvider>
        <FilterProvider>
            <App />
        </FilterProvider>
    </ProductsProvider>,


    document.getElementById('root')
)
